.START 

David Shaffer was named to the new post of executive vice president of the Maxwell Macmillan group of this communications giant.
Mr. Shaffer takes primary responsibility for the electronic and technical-services group.
He had been group vice president of the electronic-publishing group.
Also, Sheldon Aboff, formerly a vice president at Maxwell, was named group vice president with responsibility for various electronic and publishing-group companies. 

